OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham has
OL,8,Fannounced a fresh tax cut to remove
OL,9,FVAT from domestic electricity bills
OL,10,Ffrom October 1.
OL,12,FChancellor John Healey, who was
OL,13,Fappointed on Monday, said the move
OL,14,Fwould be funded by cancelling the
OL,15,FDigital ID programme announced by
OL,16,Foutgoing prime minister Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer.
OL,19,F"For too long, too many people have
OL,20,Fstruggled with the cost of living,"
OL,21,FHealey said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,F"Today's energy tax cut will give
OL,8,Ffamilies some breathing room on bills,
OL,9,Fand provide some reassurance this
OL,10,Fwinter.
OL,12,F"This measure is funded this year from
OL,13,Fcancelling the Digital ID programme,
OL,14,Fand it will help bring down inflation
OL,15,Fwhile supporting households in every
OL,16,Fpostcode."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
