OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FThe Digital ID programme was announced
OL,8,Fby former prime minister Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer, ahead of last year's Labour
OL,10,Fconference, saying it would be
OL,11,Fmandatory for right-to-work checks as
OL,12,Fpart of a crackdown on illegal
OL,13,Fimmigration.
OL,15,FBut Burnham's team has scrapped the
OL,16,Fscheme to fund the fresh tax cut.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
