CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FThe policy announcement on his first
OL,8,Ffull day in office comes after the new
OL,9,Fpremier promised to provide early
OL,10,F"breathing space" for households
OL,11,Fstruggling with the cost of living as
OL,12,Fhe stood on the steps of No 10 on
OL,13,FMonday.
OL,15,FHe said some of these measures would
OL,16,Fbe announced as early as Tuesday, when
OL,17,Fhe will chair his first cabinet
OL,18,Fmeeting.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FIn his first address to the nation as
OL,8,Fprime minister, Burnham pledged the
OL,9,Fbiggest change to British politics in
OL,10,F40 years, and said he would deliver "a
OL,11,Fnew political model and a new economic
OL,12,Fmodel" for Britain.
OL,14,FOn Monday evening, he made sweeping
OL,15,Fchanges to the Cabinet, starting with
OL,16,Fthe appointment of John Healey as the
OL,17,Fnew Chancellor to succeed Rachel
OL,18,FReeves.
OL,26,@rD@eOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FA swathe of major figures from
OL,8,FStarmer's era joined Reeves in leaving
OL,9,Fgovernment, including ex-deputy prime
OL,10,Fminister David Lammy, former attorney
OL,11,Fgeneral Lord Hermer and former housing
OL,12,Fsecretary Steve Reed.
OL,14,FTheir replacements in senior
OL,15,Fgovernment roles were announced
OL,16,Fthroughout Monday evening and will
OL,17,Fjoin Burnham around the Downing Street
OL,18,FCabinet Room table on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FLouise Haigh, a key ally of Burnham
OL,8,Fwho was instrumental in getting him
OL,9,Finto No 10, was made First Secretary
OL,10,Fof State and Chancellor of the Duchy
OL,11,Fof Lancaster, giving her a role as a
OL,12,Ffixer across government.
OL,14,FEd Miliband was appointed foreign
OL,15,Fsecretary, and Shabana Mahmood remains
OL,16,Fas home secretary, while Wes Streeting
OL,17,Fbecame the new defence secretary, and
OL,18,FAngela Rayner returned to government
OL,19,Fas housing secretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FOnce the dust had settled, it became
OL,8,Fclear that Burnham had chosen not to
OL,9,Fappoint a new deputy prime minister, a
OL,10,Fpost previously held by Rayner and
OL,11,FLammy.
OL,13,FThe Department for Science, Innovation
OL,14,Fand Technology (DSIT) was meanwhile
OL,15,Fscrapped, with responsibilities for
OL,16,Fits areas of policy assigned to other
OL,17,Fdepartments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FJonathan Reynolds was made business
OL,8,Fsecretary with a beefed-up portfolio
OL,9,Ffor his department that now includes
OL,10,Fscience and innovation, while Lisa
OL,11,FNandy remained as culture secretary
OL,12,Fwith an extended brief covering
OL,13,Fdigital.
OL,15,FA No 10 source said the new Cabinet
OL,16,Fbrought together all parts of the
OL,17,FLabour Party to deliver Burnham's
OL,18,Fagenda for the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
