CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FThose who had proven delivery and who
OL,8,Fhad the most experience had been
OL,9,Ftasked with overseeing the new Prime
OL,10,FMinister's key domestic priorities,
OL,11,Fthe source said.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
