PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FThey also pointed out that Burnham's
OL,8,FCabinet had a balanced make-up ` 50%
OL,9,Fmen, and 50% women ` and claimed that
OL,10,Fhe had boosted the number of ethnic
OL,11,Fminority members.
OL,13,FAmong the measures Burnham is
OL,14,Fexploring to help hard-pressed
OL,15,Fhouseholds with the cost of living are
OL,16,Frent controls, support for energy
OL,17,Fbills and capping the cost of bus
OL,18,Ffares.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,F"We're looking at measures that could
OL,8,Fmake a difference this year. So we are
OL,9,Flooking at all of those things, but
OL,10,Fwe'll make more announcements
OL,11,Ftomorrow," he told reporters in
OL,12,FDowning Street's rose garden on Monday.
OL,14,FA flurry of diplomatic phone calls
OL,15,Falso characterised Burnham's first day
OL,16,Fas prime minister.
OL,18,FThe first among these were calls with
OL,19,FUS President Donald Trump and
OL,20,FUkraine's President Volodymyr
OL,21,FZelenskyy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784612872
OL,3,CAndy Burnham scraps VAT on energy
OL,4,Cbills in first major policy
OL,5,Cannouncement as PM
OL,7,FIn a Truth Social post, Trump said he
OL,8,Fand the new prime minister had a "very
OL,9,Fgood conversation", adding: "The Prime
OL,10,FMinister has got a big job ahead of
OL,11,Fhim, but he will be able to do it and,
OL,12,Fof course, the U.S.A. will be there to
OL,13,Fhelp! We discussed North Sea Oil,
OL,14,FTrade, the Military Alliance, Demining
OL,15,Fof the Hormuz Strait, and many other
OL,16,Ftopics. The call was interesting, and
OL,17,Fwent very well.
OL,19,F"I wished Prime Minister Burnham, GOOD
OL,20,FLUCK AND GODSPEED!"
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@RO]qD@]OU{D@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
